            "title": "欧洲股市早段上升\r\n",
            "description": "<div id=\"newsBody\">\n<span class=\"newsDetail\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family:MingLiu;Arial;\">      欧洲股市早段上升。英国富时100指数报8,561.77点，升30.16点(0.35%)；德国DAX指数报23,461.17点，升108.48点(0.46%)；法国CAC 40指数报7,730.33点，升35.89点(0.47%)。  (WL)</span>\n</div>",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-09 15:26:32",
